            <fr:title text="Geometric interpretation of perturbations">Geometric interpretation of <fr:link href="hmlg-001C.xml" title="Perturbation of chain complex" addr="hmlg-001C" type="local">perturbations</fr:link></fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>For <fr:link href="hmlg-0013.xml" title="Algebraic cellular complex" addr="hmlg-0013" type="local">ACCs</fr:link>, the effect of a perturbation is to “reconnect” the cells. But it may not create or delete cells, since the abelian groups are unchanged.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
